t: "When he arrived at the well of Midian, he found a group of people watering ňĻtheir herdsňļ. Apart from them, he noticed two women holding back ňĻtheir herdňļ. He asked ňĻthemňļ, ‚ÄúWhat is the problem?‚ÄĚ They replied, ‚ÄúWe cannot water ňĻour animalsňļ until the ňĻotherňļ shepherds are done, for our father is a very old man.‚ÄĚ"